

1. install latest ansible version 

https://www.cyberciti.biz/faq/how-to-install-and-configure-latest-version-of-ansible-on-ubuntu-linux/

2. 

sudo useradd -m -s /bin/bash ansible
sudo passwd ansible  # Set a password (optional)
sudo usermod -aG sudo ansible  # Grant sudo access

3.

✅ Creates ansible user with sudo privileges & SSH key.
✅ Creates prometheus user (no login) and installs Prometheus as a systemd service.
✅ Creates grafana user (no login) and installs Grafana via APT repo.
✅ Ensures both services are enabled and started on boot.

4. 

✅ created ansible playbook to setup ansible user, and grafana and promethues on control VM 
✅ created ansible playbook to setup local node exporter on control VM 


